<section
  id="accueil"
  class="relative hero-bg h-screen min-h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center pt-16 md:pt-20"
>
  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1
      class="font-heading text-[1.7rem] sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 drop-shadow-md"
    >
      Ensemble, donnons à ces enfants<br class="hidden sm:block" /> une chance de réussir&nbsp;!
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-6 md:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed"
    >
      Depuis 37 ans, nous aidons des enfants défavorisés à sortir de
      l'échec scolaire. Plus de <strong class="text-white">2&nbsp;000 élèves</strong> ont pu
      retrouver le chemin de la confiance, de l'estime de soi et de la réussite.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="#apropos"
        class="px-8 py-3.5 sm:py-3 bg-white text-brand-blue font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-300 text-sm sm:text-base"
      >
        Découvrir notre mission
      </a>
      <a
        href="#faire-un-don"
        class="px-8 py-3.5 sm:py-3 bg-brand-pink text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-pink-600 transition duration-300 shadow-lg text-sm sm:text-base"
      >
        <i class="fas fa-heart mr-2"></i>Devenir Parrain
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Ocean Wave Divider — Mauritius-inspired -->
  <div class="ocean-waves">
    <svg class="wave-deep" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 180" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,80 C180,20 360,140 540,90 C720,40 900,160 1080,100 C1200,60 1320,120 1440,80 L1440,180 L0,180 Z" fill="#0e86b3" />
    </svg>
    <svg class="wave-mid" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 180" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,100 C160,60 320,140 480,110 C640,80 800,150 960,120 C1120,90 1280,130 1440,100 L1440,180 L0,180 Z" fill="#3bb4d9" />
    </svg>
    <svg class="wave-shore" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 180" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,120 C200,90 400,150 600,130 C800,110 1000,145 1200,125 C1320,115 1380,135 1440,120 L1440,180 L0,180 Z" fill="#f3f4f6" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
